# Solvo Solutions Website - Cursor Rules

## 🎯 Project Overview
We're building a **simple, professional 1-page website** for **Solvo Solutions** - an FCA-regulated claims-management firm specializing in consumer justice and redress.

### Tech Stack
- **Next.js 14** (App Router)
- **React 18** 
- **TypeScript** (for better developer experience)
- **Tailwind CSS** (for styling)
- **No backend processing** - static/client-side only

---

## 📁 Project Structure
```
solvo-website/
├── public/
│   ├── images/           # Company logos, hero images, team photos
